# Implementation Plan - Premium Modern Frontend Dashboard

Enhance the TrendScope user interface by transforming it into a high-end, premium data intelligence dashboard. We will implement modern visual design patterns (glassmorphism, vibrant gradients, premium typography, micro-interactions) and integrate the machine learning prediction endpoints into the frontend.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The updated layout will introduce a new **Machine Learning Trend Predictor** widget on the frontend. This widget calls `/api/predictions/google_spike` for keywords. Make sure the backend server is running and models are trained for the active keywords to see real probabilities (it will fall back gracefully to a message/error if models aren't trained).

## Proposed Changes

We will overhaul the CSS design tokens, HTML structure, and JS logic to implement a premium aesthetic without adding external frameworks, keeping performance high and code maintenance clean.

